nodes.name: Definition of repetition structure
nodes.fol: (forall (a e e1 c p) (iff (repetition a e e1 c p) (exists (g p1 e3) (and (repeatUntil' e3 e1 c)(executePlan e a p)(gen e3 e) (plan p a g)(subplan p1 p) (forall (e2) (if (executePlan' e2 a p1) (instance e2 e1)))))))
nodes.english: Agent a's execution e of plan p is a repetition of executions e1 until condition c is satisfied, with e3 having repeatUntil structure generating the execution

nodes.name: Definition of aRepetition
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e) (iff (aRepetition e2 e) (exists (a e1 c p) (and (repetition a e e1 c p)(instance e2 e1)))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is an instance of the body of repetitive execution e

nodes.name: Definition of startRepetition
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e) (iff (startRepetition e2 e) (exists (a e1 c p) (and (repetition a e e1 c p)(instance e2 e1) (forall (e3) (if (instance e3 e1) (or (equal e3 e2)(before e2 e3))))))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is the first repetition of the body of repetitive execution e, occurring before all other instances

nodes.name: Definition of terminateRepetition
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e) (iff (terminateRepetition e2 e) (exists (a e1 c p) (and (repetition a e e1 c p)(instance e2 e1) (forall (e3) (if (instance e3 e1) (or (equal e3 e2)(before e3 e2))))))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is the last repetition of the body of repetitive execution e, occurring after all other instances

nodes.name: Definition of intermediateRepetition
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e) (iff (intermediateRepetition e2 e) (exists (a e1 c p) (and (repetition a e e1 c p)(instance e2 e1) (not (startRepetition e2 e)) (not (terminateRepetition e2 e))))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is an intermediate repetition that is neither the first nor last instance of the body

nodes.name: Definition of completedRepetitions
nodes.fol: (forall (s e t) (iff (completedRepetitions s e t) (and (repetition a e e1 c p) (forall (e2) (iff (member e2 s) (and (aRepetition e2 e) (executed a e2 p t)))))))
nodes.english: Set s contains the repetitions of execution e that have been completed by time t

nodes.name: Definition of remainingRepetitions
nodes.fol: (forall (s e t) (iff (remainingRepetitions s e t) (and (repetition a e e1 c p) (forall (e2) (iff (member e2 s) (and (aRepetition e2 e) (not (executed a e2 p t))))))))
nodes.english: Set s contains the repetitions of execution e that remain to be executed at time t

nodes.name: Definition of currentRepetition
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e t) (iff (currentRepetition e2 e t) (exists (a e1 c p t1 t2) (and (repetition a e e1 c p)(aRepetition e2 e) (begins t1 e2)(before t1 t) (ends t2 e2)(before t t2)))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is the current repetition in repetitive execution e at time t, with t between its start and end times

nodes.name: Definition of previousRepetition
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e t) (iff (previousRepetition e2 e t) (exists (a e1 c p t2 e0 t0) (and (repetition a e e1 c p)(aRepetition e2 e) (ends t2 e2)(before t2 t) (startRepetition e0 e)(ends t0 e0)(before t0 t) (not (exists (e3 t3) (and (aRepetition e3 e)(nequal e3 e2) (ends t3 e3)(before t2 t3) (before t3 t))))))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is the most recent repetition that ended before time t, with no other repetitions ending between e2 and t

nodes.name: Definition of nextRepetition
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e t) (iff (nextRepetition e2 e t) (exists (a e1 c p t2 e0 t0) (and (repetition a e e1 c p)(aRepetition e2 e) (begins t2 e2)(before t t2) (terminateRepetition e0 e)(begins t0 e0) (before t t0) (not (exists (e3 t3) (and (aRepetition e3 e)(nequal e3 e2) (begins t3 e3)(before t3 t2) (before t t3))))))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is the next repetition that begins after time t, with no other repetitions beginning between t and e2

nodes.name: Definition of repetitionsCount
nodes.fol: (forall (n e t) (iff (repetitionsCount n e t) (exists (a e1 c p s) (and (repetition a e e1 c p) (completedRepetitions s e t)(card n s)))))
nodes.english: Integer n is the number of repetitions of execution e that have been completed by time t

nodes.name: Definition of iterationThru
nodes.fol: (forall (e e1 x s s1) (iff (iterationThru e e1 x s s1) (and (arg* x e1)(sequence s)(sequence s1) (forall (y) (if (inSeq y s)(instance y x))) (forall (e2 n) (iff (nth e2 n s1) (exists (y) (and (nth y n s) (subst x e1 y e2))))))))
nodes.english: Execution e is an iteration through sequence s where entity x in body e1 is substituted by successive elements of s to create sequence s1 of instantiated executions

nodes.name: Definition of startIterationThru
nodes.fol: (forall (e2 e) (iff (startIterationThru e2 e) (exists (e1 x s s1) (and (iterationThru e e1 x s s1)(first e2 s1)))))
nodes.english: Execution e2 is the first iteration in the iterationThru e, being the first element in the sequence of iterations

nodes.name: Definition of completedIterationsThru
nodes.fol: (forall (s0 e t) (iff (completedIterationsThru s0 e t) (exists (e1 x s s1) (and (iterationThru e e1 x s s1) (forall (e2) (iff (member e2 s0) (exists (t2) (and (member e2 s1)(ends t2 e2) (before t2 t)))))))))
nodes.english: Set s0 contains the iterations through e that have been completed by time t

nodes.name: Definition of doNextIterationThru'
nodes.fol: (forall (e3 a e t) (iff (doNextIterationThru' e3 a e t) (exists (e1 x s s1 p) (and (iterationThru e e1 x s s1) (execute a e3 p) (nextRepetition e3 e t)))))
nodes.english: Action e3 is agent a's execution of the next iteration in the iterationThru e at time t

nodes.name: Definition of abortIterationThru
nodes.fol: (forall (a e t) (iff (abortIterationThru a e t) (exists (e1 x s s1 p) (and (iterationThru e e1 x s s1) (executePlan' e a p) (abort a p t)))))
nodes.english: Agent a aborts iterationThru e at time t before completing the entire sequence of entities

nodes.name: Definition of completeIterationThru
nodes.fol: (forall (a e t) (iff (completeIterationThru a e t) (exists (e1 x s s1 p) (and (iterationThru e e1 x s s1) (executePlan' e a p) (executedPlan a p t)))))
nodes.english: Agent a completes iterationThru e at time t when all entities in the sequence have been processed
